{"tid":1167097,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國一晶片初創企業 控華為高層涉偷商業機密","createTime":"2019-05-23T00:23:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T02:19:17.000Z","uid":48083,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c5d0de4c8e59f7a878cc874cd7b61fe92a25e0d6","tid":1167097,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T00:23:00.000Z","msg":"《華爾街日報》引述法庭文件稱，美國一間晶片初創企業指控華為副董事長Eric Xu，涉及合謀偷取該公司的商業機密。<br />\n<br />\n案件將於6月3日在得克薩斯州聯邦法庭開審。<br />\n<br />\n原訴CNEX Labs指控華為在中國一間大學協助下，涉及進行為期多年的合謀行動，偷取集團的機密。根據CNEX陳述的案情，該公司正研發一項有助數據中心所用電腦硬件提升效能的技術，華為在一名中國大學教授協助下，非法掌握了有關技術。CNEX與華為自2017年開始便出現爭拗。<br />\n<br />\n華為與CNEX未有回應傳媒相關查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2144208\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2144208&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1Uoyo1HO27hz5fVRhbnvZL2FK%2Bg%3D&h=59073975\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2144208</a>"},{"pid":"ead5c9878a7c651797af245162698b0aa19b0c5f","tid":1167097,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T00:30:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af6e0914fa6393cad55d9afc28b7cb1c48a524fa","tid":1167097,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T00:50:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">美初創公司指控華為副董事長參與竊取其商業機密</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n法院文件顯示，微軟和戴爾科技集團支持的一家矽谷晶片初創公司指控華為技術有限公司副董事長徐直軍參與竊取其商業機密的行動。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">2019年5月23日08:03 CST 更新</span><br />\n<br />\n法院文件顯示，微軟(Microsoft Corp., MSFT)和戴爾科技集團(Dell Technologies Inc., DELL)支持的一家矽谷晶片初創公司指控華為技術有限公司(Huawei Technologies Co.)副董事長徐直軍(Eric Xu)參與竊取其商業機密的行動。<br />\n<br />\n這起訴訟將於6月3日在得州東區聯邦法院開庭。總部位於加州的CNEX Labs Inc.在訴訟中指控，華為多年來密謀竊取其固態硬碟電腦存儲技術，一家中國大學也是同謀。<br />\n<br />\n華為對涉及徐直軍的指控不予置評。法院文件顯示，華為否認訴訟中提出的任何不當行為指控，並且反控CNEX竊取該中國公司的商業機密。<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.wsj.com/articles/%E7%BE%8E%E5%88%9D%E5%89%B5%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E5%89%AF%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B%E9%95%B7%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E7%AB%8A%E5%8F%96%E5%85%B6%E5%95%86%E6%A5%AD%E6%A9%9F%E5%AF%86-121558569291\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.wsj.com%2Farticles%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2588%259D%25E5%2589%25B5%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258E%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%2582%25BA%25E5%2589%25AF%25E8%2591%25A3%25E4%25BA%258B%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%2588%2587%25E7%25AB%258A%25E5%258F%2596%25E5%2585%25B6%25E5%2595%2586%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25AF%2586-121558569291&d=z4MUysNBbosN1Ywc1Uoyo1HO27hz5fVRhbnvZL2FK%2Bg%3D&h=1e68db6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cn.wsj.com/articles/%E7%BE%8E%E5%88%9D%E5%89%B5%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BA%E5%89%AF%E8%91%A3%E4%BA%8B%E9%95%B7%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E7%AB%8A%E5%8F%96%E5%85%B6%E5%95%86%E6%A5%AD%E6%A9%9F%E5%AF%86-121558569291</a>"},{"pid":"1666edfe0d23e37644114866818d81a1b3a05f8b","tid":1167097,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T00:51:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91f7e2d661a8713f5a8478a202d7cd2ff140a83a","tid":1167097,"uid":47080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T01:02:21.000Z","msg":"亮劍"},{"pid":"596b574472e7126c11e59fb1a046d6ba9fde0e26","tid":1167097,"uid":64191,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T01:05:34.000Z","msg":"之前已經聽過，中國一直以黎積極參與新創企業既展覽會、交流會，趁機在場偷取技術、挖角及資訊，或者借合作獨吞，新創企業要錢要支持，好易中伏"},{"pid":"7379603f43dadee761aaee35dc9e6edf536a4e2a","tid":1167097,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T01:18:25.000Z","msg":"法院文件顯示，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>微軟和戴爾科技集團支持的一家矽谷晶片初創公司</strong></span></span>指控華為技術有限公司副董事長徐直軍參與竊取其商業機密的行動。"},{"pid":"90aa9852e284357c694012683f66c9706d2